-- Merkel Says Cutting Deficits Essential, Issue to Be Controversial at G-20
-- Rainer Buergin
-- 2010-06-24T14:05:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/merkel-says-cutting-deficits-essential-issue-to-be-controversial-at-g-20.html

          
          
             Chancellor Angela Merkel said it’s
“absolutely necessary” to reduce budget deficits to put
economies back on a stable footing, adding she expects
controversy on that issue between Group of 20 nations at a
meeting of leaders in Toronto this week.  
          
          


  


        